Package: algebraicodin
Title: Compositional Epidemiological Modeling with odin2
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Simon", "Frost", email = "sdwfrost@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5207-9879"))
Description: Compositional model building using applied category theory,
    targeting the odin2 DSL for high-performance simulation via dust2.
    Supports Petri nets, stock-flow diagrams, open systems, and
    composition via undirected wiring diagrams. Generates both
    deterministic (ODE) and stochastic (discrete-time) odin2 code.
    Port of AlgebraicPetri.jl and StockFlow.jl from the AlgebraicJulia
    ecosystem.
